        "link": "https://lora-alliance.org/about-lorawan",
        "description": "The largest overhead for a network of thousands of devices across a vast geographical area is the ability to get a communications signal or the cost associated with it. Traditionally we have used mobile telephony networks, however I am exploring the use of LoRaWAN, a protocol boasting a long-range and small bandwidth. Glasgow already boasts a large network and both SWAN & CENSIS <a href=\"#swan-iot-proposal\" aria-describedby=\"footnote-label\">recently announced their plans to continue the expansion of LoRaWAN</a>.",
